üöÄ Final Recommendation (For Large Volume Regression Updates)

If you are updating test case status in bulk:

Use token-based auth (NOT password)

Use connection pooling (requests.Session())

Implement retry logic (429, 5xx handling)

Use batching (don‚Äôt update one-by-one if API supports bulk)

